        public void buy(Product product,
                int amount)
        Buys a product: Checks if the amount to buy is lower than Product.getFreeSpace() if available space is lower than amount ordered then it'll buy the remaining amount left. Afterwards a new state is calculated.

        amount - Amount of products for stockmovement - varies on method
